_:Ncedf9835464c43989e1522307054e0ec <http://schema.org/articleBody> "<div class=\"govspeak\">\n<h2 id=\"what-we-do\">What we do</h2>\n\n<p><a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?si=ntCkwzqcJHE3AYSO&amp;v=eXfsr_VtjSM&amp;feature=youtu.be\">What we deliver every day</a> (Youtube video)</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"doing-business-with-dio---entering-the-supply-chain\">Doing business with <abbr title=\"Defence Infrastructure Organisation\">DIO</abbr> - entering the supply chain</h2>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>\n    <p><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/ministry-of-defence/about/procurement\">Procurement at <abbr title=\"Ministry of Defence\">MOD</abbr></a>: This page outlines the many ways in which you can do business with the Ministry of Defence.</p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p><a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.find-tender.service.gov.uk/\">Find a Tender</a>: This central digital platform is where suppliers submit their core business information, which is then shared across multiple bids and customers.</p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p><a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.crowncommercial.gov.uk/information-for-buyers-and-suppliers/start-supplying\">CCS (Crown Commercial Services) Frameworks</a>: Search for existing suppliers on relevant frameworks and lots. To become a supplier through CCS you have to respond to a contract notice and succeed in the tender process. Details of how to register your interest in a tender are contained in the contract notice.</p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p><a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://forms.office.com/pages/responsepage.aspx?id=7WB3vlNZS0iuldChbfoJ5QZ1XaOZ5HBDguEU0NG4CFdURDJFTjZMRVZSUlFQU0xMOUlTSlQ3RUgxSy4u\"><abbr title=\"Defence Infrastructure Organisation\">DIO</abbr> Opt in for Updates and Events</a>: By completing this short opt in form you will be added to the mailing list to receive <abbr title=\"Defence Infrastructure Organisation\">DIO</abbr> and event notifications.</p>\n  </li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2 id=\"follow-us\">Follow us</h2>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>Read the <a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://insidedio.blog.gov.uk/\">Inside <abbr title=\"Defence Infrastructure Organisation\">DIO</abbr> blog</a>\n</li>\n  <li>Watch our <a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/@DIO_MOD\">YouTube videos</a>\n</li>\n  <li>Follow us on Twitter at <a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.twitter.com/mod_dio\">mod_DIO</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n\n</div>" .
